snippet.title: HappyFunland - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Get spooked with this creepy trailer for HappyFunland, the upcoming horror VR game set in an abandoned theme park filled with terrifying rides and the ghosts of a tragic past.

#SummerOfGaming #IGN
